                Οὐαλέριος ἐμῷ Θεοδού <supplied reason="lost">λῳ. Τόδε μέν μνῆμα</supplied> <lb n="2"/>ἐμόν· ἡ δὲ δόξα σή· μαθ<supplied reason="lost">έτωσαν οὖν παῖδες</supplied> <lb n="3"/>τοὺς θρέψαντας φιλ<supplied reason="lost">εῖν· χάριν ἔχω σοι</supplied> <lb n="4"/>καὶ ζῶν καὶ ἀναπαυό <supplied reason="lost">μενος διὰ πα</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>ντός <expan><abbr>Valer</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">meo Theodu</supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/>lo haec <supplied reason="lost">memoria</supplied> <lb n="7"/>quidem me<supplied reason="lost">a tua autem laus</supplied> <lb n="8"/>discant igit<supplied reason="lost">ur pueri</supplied> <lb n="9"/>nutritores a<supplied reason="lost">mare gratiam habeo ti</supplied><lb break="no" n="10"/>bi vivus et qu<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">iescens in perpetuum</supplied>
